{"tid":351516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無業漢$5000賄考官判囚　圖考車牌自食其力","createTime":"2017-08-08T06:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T10:30:27.000Z","uid":33643,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfcbcad90bc0fc7c4bbfcb56415061442954f51c","tid":351516,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:15:23.000Z","msg":"廉政公署早前落案起訴一名男子，指他涉嫌以一封5000港元利是行賄運輸署一名考牌主任，以求取得駕駛考試合格。42歲無業男被告張欣早前承認一項向公職人員提供利益罪，今天(8日)在觀塘法院被判即時監禁半年。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官判刑時表示，行賄公職人員是嚴重罪行，必須嚴懲以儆效尤，<span style=\"color: red;\">被告所為愚蠢自私</span>，衝擊運輸署的考牌制度，對其他考生不公平，而且一旦被告的計劃成功，將危及其他道路使用者的安全。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指事件不幸，<span style=\"color: red;\">患精神病已10年</span>的被告今次犯案，乃因家人過於愛護，故試圖考取車牌藉此「走出社會，不靠家人」。被告母親撰寫求情信自責照顧不周，冀能陪伴兒子繼續治療精神問題。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告於今年4月5日向運輸署一名二級考牌主任提供利益，即一封5000港元的利是，作為將其私家車駕駛考試的駕駛技巧及表現評為合格的報酬。廉署早前接獲運輸署轉介的貪污投訴，展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170808/photo/bkn-20170808114810197-0808_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170808122427\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170808%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170808114810197-0808_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170808122427&h=65f471fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n42歲(賄賂)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d651767279a15438068d7be56faadda340312593","tid":351516,"uid":115525,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:17:17.000Z","msg":"宜家用5千蚊 包食包住半年<br />\n佢都算達到自食其力既目標呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f5abc17991daedf3496ca18f10d42b53b0e401","tid":351516,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"蘋果好似話係自動波"},{"pid":"5ab871b6b3b6e4a657761f76161400749ee875b0","tid":351516,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502164305_fcec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502164305_fcec.jpg&h=4a3ab80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cc601bd196aee45a24b914203f9f2a4bc72cf0","tid":351516,"uid":24165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:20:34.000Z","msg":"d狗官貪污又唔見會判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75c76985921263ca55cc05909b69168cc341bed","tid":351516,"uid":131526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502164305_fcec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502164305_fcec.jpg&h=4a3ab80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4edc44cf2ce0bff9442732f80b551290aa0a66","tid":351516,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:21:27.000Z","msg":"被告家人<span style=\"color: red;\">承諾提醒被告服藥</span>及協助他重投社會。被告母親在求情信自責照顧不周，<span style=\"color: red;\">指被告愚鈍</span>但孝順，非大奸大惡。被告女兒與前妻同住，他亦想做一個盡責爸爸。母親信中續指，最大心願是被告康復，被告不想胞姊供養，「想做番啲嘢」才導致犯案。<br />\n<br />\n案情指被告今年4月5日在運輸署油塘駕駛中心，向監考的二級考牌主任丘冠熙<span style=\"color: red;\">提供紅包稱是見面禮。丘兩度拒絕接受，被告強行塞在寫字板上</span>，丘打開發現內有現金5,000元，向上級報告和廉署舉報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd58a76752e026028d72eef8040493059bb3cd56","tid":351516,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"去大陸咁做咪無事"},{"pid":"10c808d98847289f5558ff15327704cd2a450be1","tid":351516,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"稱不想再由姊姊照顧<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指被告的父母及3位姊姊及外甥均有到庭，並為被告撰寫求情信，他們自責未有好好照顧被告，但指被告自小孝順，品格良好，犯案只是不想再被姊姊照顧，而<span style=\"color: red;\">案發時沒有發病</span>。<br />\n<br />\n第二次考試把紅包交考牌官<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告於今年4月5日到運輸署油塘駕駛考試中心<span style=\"color: red;\">第二次參加私家車路試</span>，被告登記後登上一輛私家車。當考牌主任上車時，被告向他提供一個紅包，並說<span style=\"color: red;\">「阿Sir，見面禮，請收下。」</span>雖然考牌主任拒絕接受，但被告再次向他提供紅包。<br />\n<br />\n對考牌主任稱是見面禮<br />\n<br />\n當考牌主任查核被告的香港身份證及學習駕駛執照時，被告將紅包放在考牌主任的寫字夾板上，並再說：「阿Sir，見面禮，請收下。」<br />\n<br />\n當考牌主任打開紅包，發現內裏有數張1000元鈔票。考牌主任隨即向中心主管報告事件，廉署其後接獲舉報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797ee0a44230b0526e3d928da689f8487da403f1","tid":351516,"uid":521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:26:49.000Z","msg":"其實幾可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e8fd046dced0c2c5689ebf5857c82343eec82a","tid":351516,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502164305_fcec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502164305_fcec.jpg&h=4a3ab80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258c7679ca0ccbe47018fe0e9f62f534487c709f","tid":351516,"uid":39668,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:29:12.000Z","msg":"連車牌都考唔到既人真心要拎入毒氣室度毒撚死曬佢地"},{"pid":"46af6b6af19eab59ac9c3c2ec7a5b2eba3a4eb33","tid":351516,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0a00978811a342c87f6982c785c3afe9614650","tid":351516,"uid":31780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講埋佢係邊種精神病, 我擔心佢揸揸下車發病... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63294ec95f3b4707add0cafe5032b2ec84ca7ad","tid":351516,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"紅咩包呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"047906011779a8036803f65af36268cab10e1d5a","tid":351516,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"果然愚鈍，做乜唔去大陸考？"},{"pid":"4934e577c578a5a0c48c864c5e8813bb8c91dd31","tid"